WEBVTT

00:00:59.968 --> 00:01:01.786
He wouldn't get up.

00:01:01.810 --> 00:01:05.285
They dragged me away.
I didn't want to leave him."

00:01:06.856 --> 00:01:10.047
And I say to Amanda,

00:01:12.253 --> 00:01:14.226
"The last time you saw Alex,

00:01:15.229 --> 00:01:16.726
was he bleeding?

00:01:17.607 --> 00:01:23.734
Did you have any of his blood on you?"

00:01:24.855 --> 00:01:29.139
And she cries, "Yeah, a lot,"

00:01:29.163 --> 00:01:30.805
and breaks down.